metadata.description: Hour Loop, Inc., an online retailer, engages in e-commerce retailing in the United States. The company sells home/garden dcor, toys, kitchenware, apparel, and electronics products. It sells its products through hourloop.com, amazon.com, and walmart.com. Hour Loop, Inc. was founded in 2013 and is headquartered in Redmond, Washington.
